{"tid":983252,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"BTS歌迷隨地放行李，因為日本治安太好","createTime":"2019-01-15T20:56:37.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-16T03:02:05.000Z","uid":4618,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"583ff510ea5ff2870cd8f833b69cebf99df64ca0","tid":983252,"uid":4618,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-15T20:56:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/01/16/045018_e481d9fd15e4058f4ec6e7770336ce39.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F01%2F16%2F045018_e481d9fd15e4058f4ec6e7770336ce39.png&h=52dee116&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n如果大家曾經試過剛下飛機就直奔演唱會，或者在日本留學時遠征看演唱會，就會知道演唱會場地附近的置物櫃有多搶手。即日來回的外國歌迷和非當地居民的日本歌迷都是你的競爭對手，所以如果想寄存行李，就要盡早到會場附近租用置物櫃。萬一找不到可用的置物櫃，大家會怎麼辦呢？<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/01/16/045050_4a319105cb4e1d1f4c775cb8540a7868.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F01%2F16%2F045050_4a319105cb4e1d1f4c775cb8540a7868.png&h=c45d9860&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n近日，網民在名古屋巨蛋鄰近車站的置物櫃附近，發現有大量行李。剛好當天是BTS防彈少年團的名古屋巨蛋演唱會，故網民猜測是歌迷的行李。由於歌迷把行李放在車站，有什麼萬一都可以向站務員報失，變相站務員和附近商店的店員無端端要替他們看守行李。<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/01/16/045127_e7a178093a9bbd3c5a2f79518b9ce86f.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F01%2F16%2F045127_e7a178093a9bbd3c5a2f79518b9ce86f.png&h=cc38f98b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▼ 公眾電話被包圍&hellip;&hellip;<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/01/16/045210_e35ab8164767f6f67c486471c78898a5.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F01%2F16%2F045210_e35ab8164767f6f67c486471c78898a5.png&h=b8d9cf79&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n部份網民留言指，「大概是首次遠征的人沒有想過置物櫃會那麼搶手吧」。的確，即使事前在網上看置物櫃攻略，也未必能夠保證有置物櫃可用。但是又想用行李箱帶演唱會商品回家，到底可以怎樣做呢？<br />\n<br />\n個人認為ecbo cloak是非常方便的解決方法。它被稱為行李界的airbnb，提供平台讓商店租出寄放行李的位置，例如咖啡店和郵局等。而且，顧客可以用智能手機提前預約寄存位置，並使用信用卡進行簡單付款，價錢跟投幣式儲物櫃一樣，小型行李300円，大型行李600円。<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/01/16/045257_fc95cdc604498d3929d2dd0e21d0c00b.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F01%2F16%2F045257_fc95cdc604498d3929d2dd0e21d0c00b.png&h=af8b5288&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n比起四處找儲物櫃，這個服務方便得多呢！<br />\n<br />\n<em>轉japhub日本集合<br />\n<a href=\"https://japhub.com/?c=8887\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fjaphub.com%2F%3Fc%3D8887&d=yy9IwgYhyIKe5sLzLST0ITQ9OVC7k%2FvddpU5ARN7O10%3D&h=0dcd69a0\" target=\"_blank\">https://japhub.com/?c=8887</a></em>"},{"pid":"42b6507357aa369cfb06396b645e33038c9daed3","tid":983252,"uid":208722,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-15T21:00:58.000Z","msg":"玷汙日本列土嘅畜牲"},{"pid":"1355260ec85017093e7881ac29cca97260e1381f","tid":983252,"uid":4618,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-16T02:56:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b0cdbbe1b6ef10112728645376476d3e64dc6b54","tid":983252,"uid":13504,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-16T02:58:55.000Z","msg":"由於歌迷把行李放在車站，<span style=\"color: red;\">有什麼萬一都可以向站務員報失</span>，變相站務員和附近商店的店員無端端要替他們看守行李。<br />\n<br />\n見到呢句就諗起香港人實有份"},{"pid":"cb03f582e7a93ac9efc06d26cddfa08ef7b3b9d8","tid":983252,"uid":89931,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-16T03:02:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 韓狗"}]}